data.description: Stunning impeccably maintained 4 BR, 2 BA home has been renovated from top to bottom! Let's not forget the new 40x60 steel gar. w/16' sidewalls, 14' overhead doors, power, concrete slab, workbench & shelves. Great for all the toys! Home is light & bright throughout, gorgeous interior w/greatroom, porcelain ceramic tile flooring, white cabinetry, center island w/seating, granite counters, SS appliances, perfect for your family to congregate and entertain. Main floor office/bedroom, fully finished basement walks up to 2 car att. gar.  So many updates w/all new flooring throughout, LP smart siding, new natural gas forced air/central, renovated LL bath, new hot tub enclosure & hot tub included, water softener, water heater & pressure tank!  Fantastic location just outside of Danbury on 2.83 beautifully wooded acres, UTV/snowmobile trails right out your back door, hundreds of acres of county land nearby, St. Croix River and the list goes on!  Make this your Northwoods home or retreat!
